import Vue from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from '@/router'
import Header from '@/components/Header'
Vue.config.productionTip = false
Vue.component('Header',Header)
new Vue({
  render: h => h(App),
  router: router
}).$mount('#app')
